## Compliance
- **Attribution**: All files include the mandatory VS 2082 | 2026-03-07 headers.
- **No Local Storage**: Tokens are strictly handled in memory-only closures within [auth.js](file:///d:/IMP/GitHub/ganitsutram/websites/ui-core/js/auth.js).
- **UI Core Integration**: Externalized all styles and logic into the platform's shared assets.
